data.description: Discover charm and comfort in this beautiful 3-bedroom home with a loft in the heart of Haymount. Elegant hardwood floors and plush new carpeting create a warm atmosphere throughout. 2022 Roof and 2023 Central AC, The kitchen boasts modern granite countertops, perfect for both cooking and entertaining. Outback you have a wired shop ready to use for all your needs. Enjoy the convenience of being close to shopping and restaurants and all down town has to offer, making this residence not just a home but a lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this house your own retreat in a vibrant community
